        <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">hypercalcemia</ENAMEX>. In contrast, <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">hypercalcemia</ENAMEX> frequently
        <ENAMEX TYPE="DISEASE">complicates congenital lactase deficiency</ENAMEX> [ <ENAMEX TYPE="LAW">4</ENAMEX> ] . The
